original_title: The Making of the Philadelphia Eagles Cheerleaders Lingerie Calendar 2005-2006
overview: The Philadelphia Eagles Cheerleaders made national headlines by being the first squad in the NFL to produce a lingerie calendar. Now you have exclusive behind the scenes access into the making of the highly publicized, cutting-edge calendar!  This DVD gives you an up close and personal look at the actual photo shoots of thirty-eight of the most beautiful cheerleaders in the NFL as they model sexy, designer lingerie.
title: The Making of the Philadelphia Eagles Cheerleaders Lingerie Calendar 2005-2006
